iSQL> -- Crash repro converted from legacy sql harness.
iSQL> -- Original semantics preserved:
iSQL> --   1) only LOOP expansion changed
iSQL> --   2) repeated INSERT statements remain separate executions
iSQL> --   3) SELECT shape and hint text are kept close to the source
iSQL> -- Expected on affected build:
iSQL> --   abnormal termination / server disconnect during one of the SELECT statements
